timeline.bodyText:
Not in the constructor. You should always decouple object instantiation from doing "real" work. Particularly if its something hardcore like reading big files from disk.
A better pattern would be to use this class like:
Classifier classifier = new TensorflowClassifier();
classifier.loadModels();

